.claude/settings.local.json
# `.claude/rules/` holds workspace refresh artifacts (written by
# `macf rules refresh`), not source. Canonical rule files live at
# `plugin/rules/`. Without this ignore, the refresh-produced copy
# appears as a persistent untracked file and causes `macf self-update`
# to refuse with a dirty-tree error. Both agents hit this same day
# — see `project_untracked_coordination_artifact.md`.
.claude/rules/
node_modules/
dist/
*.log
.env
.env.local
coverage/
.worktrees/
*.pem
